steps.name: And  user clicks on Sign in link in the Home page
Then  the page title should be displayed as "Login"
When  the user enters valid Username and Password from "Login" and 0 in the Login form
And  user clicks on Login button
Then  the page title should be displayed as "NumpyNinja"
And  user should successfully logged in and get success message from "Login" and 0
Then  the user should see the username in the top right corner
When  the user clicks on Sign out link in home page after successful logged in
Then  the user should be able to logged out and get success message from "Login" and 0
